org.cloudbus.foggatewaylib.core

Class Store<T extends Data>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudbus.foggatewaylib.core.Store<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the Data type this Store stores.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    InMemoryStore

    public abstract class Store<T extends Data>
extends java.lang.Object
    Collection of Data sorted by their id.

    Inside the ExecutionManager, there may be different Stores of the same Data since each store is identified by an outputKey, which identifies the data flow it stores.

    Author:
    Riccardo Mancini
